snippet.title: Overwatch 2 x Cowboy Bebop | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as the legendary Bebop crew in Overwatch 2 x Cowboy Bebop

Hunt down your bounty with the effortlessly cool Cassidy as Spike, Ashe as Faye, Mauga as Jet, Sombra as Ed, and earn a free skin of Wrecking Ball as Ein by playing games and completing challenges.

Hop in and play Overwatch 2 x Cowboy Bebop when it arrives March 12!

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!
_
